The 3 main, formal UK reports addressing the 2001 FMD outbreak, were:
1. Report of the policy commission on the future of farming and food,
January 2002
<http://archive.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/farming/pdf/PC%20Report2.pdf>
2. Inquiry on Infectious Diseases in Livestock, the Royal Society, July 2002
<http://www.royalsoc.ac.uk/inquiry/index.html>
3. Lessons to be Learned Inquiry Report (chaired by Dr Iain
Anderson), July 2002
<http://archive.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/fmd/fmd_report/report/index.htm>.
